Scenario: Lin is using the PathToSuccess platform to set a daily schedule of everything that he needs to do to have better time
management, plus he is going through some of the AI feautures and making notifications for scholarship opportunities and internships.

User story: Lin is a student at the University of Charlotte. He is a senior and about to graduate but does not know 
what he needs to do in order to accomplish his dreams. He just wants a job that makes money, have a nice car, house, 
and beautiful girlfriend. He heard about PathToSuccess through a friend and wants to try the product out so he can manage his time better.

Feature list: optimal sequence of courses, extracurricular activities, and internships to align with students' schedule
campus resources, including academic advisors, career counselors, and tutoring services
templates and tips for creating standout job application material.
